datoCmsKey.name: Meg Elliott
datoCmsKey.bio:
Organizing, inspiring and leading others is my call.

There is, and has always been, something inside that yearns to bring people together, organize them, harness their collective energy, assume responsibility, make decisions, and lead them on a meaningful and challenging quest. My work in user experience and user interface design has intertwined my passions for art and human behavior with an expression of my essential nature to lead.
